				<p>I've been around long enough to know what actually works and what's just hype. Built QuranGallery from zero to 25K users, so I understand both the technical and product sides. I don't just write code - I think about whether it'll actually solve your problem.</p>
				<p>Plus, I've made enough mistakes to help you avoid the common ones.</p>
			</blockquote>
			
			<div class="two-column">
				<div class="highlight-box success">
					<h3>📈 QuranGallery.app Metrics</h3>
					<ul>
						<li>🚀 <strong>25K+ active users</strong> (55% DAU)</li>
						<li>🤖 <strong>AI-powered features</strong>: Verse explanation, Q&A bot</li>
						<li>⚡ <strong>Stack</strong>: Next.js, Node, OpenAI, Pinecone</li>
						<li>💯 <strong>97% user satisfaction</strong> (NPS survey)</li>
						<li>💰 <strong>40%+ AI cost reduction</strong> for enterprise clients</li>
						<li>🔍 <strong>10+ years</strong> production experience</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
				
				<div class="highlight-box info">
					<h3>⚡ Fast & Efficient</h3>
					<ul>
						<li>Quick turnaround times</li>
						<li>Clear communication</li>
						<li>No BS, just solutions</li>
						<li>Production-ready code</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- Recruiter CTA Section -->
		<section id="recruiters" class="section">
			<div class="cta-box">
				<h2>📨 Hiring Managers & Recruiters</h2>
				<p>I'm currently accepting:</p>
				<ul style="text-align: left; max-width: 400px; margin: 0 auto;">
					<li>🤖 <strong>AI Integration Projects</strong></li>
					<li>💻 <strong>Full-Stack Development Roles</strong></li>
					<li>🔍 <strong>Technical Consulting</strong></li>
					<li>🌐 <strong>Remote AI Solutions</strong></li>
